  100 entries only
- changed default process/verbose to 0 for radiative_decay

27th June 2000  John Allison  (test18-V01-01-07)
- Added /control/verbose 2 to *.in.

27th June 2000  John Allison  (test18-V01-01-06)
- Added test18.large_N.in.

